snippet.title: Chad S. Keller: Beyond Avery Road
snippet.description:
Beyond Avery Road 
Investigative Journalist Chad Keller from Atlanta, Georgia and Wisconsin Political Insider Juan Tescrue bring you the unheard political story of Steven Avery.

Is Steven Avery a Political Prisoner? 
Did Steven Drizin Purposely leave out evidence that could have sent Brendan Dassey home at the En Banc?
